==========
    Oligonychus - A spider written in Perl 5, used for fetching schedules of various TV channels in India
==========

    This code was developed By Azri
    You can redistribute it and/or modify it under either the terms of the GPL version 2 (see the file GPL).

    Usage: 
    	   ./bin/spider.ksh 

    Requires:

            Perl 5 and associated perl modules
	    ksh -- yeah.. we like ksh as our shell... we are children of the "korn"! ;-)

	    If you want to enable indexing of the schedule then you need to install http://xapian.org/.
